ARM: OMAP: board-am3517evm: Configure McBSP1 CLKR/FSR signal source

am3517evm board uses McBSP1 for audio with 4pin configuration.
The CLKR/FSR signals need to be connected to CLKX/FSX pin of the SoC in
this case.

